---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import MeshBackground from '../../components/MeshBackground.jsx';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Virtual Power Plant Platform | Mehdi Bamou"
  description="Strategic enterprise architecture for renewable energy transformation - Virtual Power Plant platform leveraging IoT, AI/ML, and cloud infrastructure"
  path="/projects/vpp-platform"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative py-16 md:py-24 bg-white overflow-hidden">
    <MeshBackground variant="primary" client:load />
    
    <div class="container-custom relative z-10">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <a href="/portfolio" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary hover:underline mb-6">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18" />
          </svg>
          Back to Portfolio
        </a>
        
        <div class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-primary/10 rounded-full mb-4">
          <span class="text-sm font-medium text-primary">Strategic Architecture & Digital Transformation</span>
        </div>
        
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900 leading-tight">
          Virtual Power Plant (VPP) Platform
        </h1>
        
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Orchestrated enterprise-wide strategic planning and deployment of Virtual Power Plant infrastructure, aligning technology roadmap with corporate sustainability vision and market positioning
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span>2022 - 2024</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-slate-600">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M21 13.255A23.931 23.931 0 0112 15c-3.183 0-6.22-.62-9-1.745M16 6V4a2 2 0 00-2-2h-4a2 2 0 00-2 2v2m4 6h.01M5 20h14a2 2 0 002-2V8a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
            </svg>
            <span>Enterprise Architect</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Image -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl">
        <img 
          src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509391366360-2e959784a276?w=1200&h=600&fit=crop" 
          alt="Solar panels and renewable energy infrastructure"
          class="w-full h-[400px] object-cover"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Company Context -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
          Company Context
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-12">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Company</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Sunvigo GmbH</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Industry</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Renewable Energy / Green Technology</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Company Size</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">Mid-size Enterprise (200-500 employees)</p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Location</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600">KÃ¶ln, Germany</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Overview -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
          Project Overview
        </h2>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Led the strategic planning, development, and deployment of a Virtual Power Plant (VPP) platform that revolutionized how the company manages distributed energy resources. This initiative aligned technology strategy with the corporate vision for a sustainable energy future while establishing market leadership in renewable energy management.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            The platform leverages IoT technology to connect and manage solar PV systems across multiple locations, enabling real-time monitoring, control, and optimization of energy production and distribution. By implementing advanced AI and machine learning algorithms, we achieved predictive energy demand forecasting and intelligent distribution optimization.
          </p>
          
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
            Successfully engaged with diverse stakeholders including regulatory bodies, energy providers, and community representatives to ensure project alignment with industry standards, compliance requirements, and community needs.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Responsibilities -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
          Key Responsibilities & Leadership
        </h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">
                Strategic Architecture Leadership
              </h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                Coordinated enterprise-wide strategic planning, aligning technology roadmap with business objectives and sustainability goals. Established architecture governance frameworks and decision-making processes.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">
                Stakeholder Engagement & Alignment
              </h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                Engaged with regulatory bodies, energy providers, technology partners, and community stakeholders to ensure compliance with industry standards and alignment with community needs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-primary/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 19v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2zm0 0V9a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v10m-6 0a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2v14a2 2 0 01-2 2h-2a2 2 0 01-2-2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">
                Technology Innovation & AI/ML Implementation
              </h3>
              <p class="text-slate-600">
                Implemented AI and machine learning algorithms for predictive energy demand forecasting, intelligent distribution optimization, and operational cost reduction, achieving 25% improvement in system efficiency.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Technologies & Architecture -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
          Technologies & Architecture
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">Cloud & Infrastructure</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">AWS</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Kubernetes</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">GitOps</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">ArgoCD</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Crossplane</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">IoT & Real-time</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">IoT Integration</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Real-time Analytics</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Device Management</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card">
            <h3 class="font-heading font-bold mb-3 text-slate-900">AI & Optimization</h3>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">AI/ML</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Forecasting</span>
              <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-primary/10 text-primary rounded-full text-sm">Optimization</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Outcomes & Impact -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-slate-900">
          Outcomes & Business Impact
        </h2>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-emerald-50 border-green-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">25% Efficiency Improvement</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Achieved significant improvement in system efficiency through AI-driven optimization and real-time management</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 border-blue-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">30% Cost Reduction</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Reduced operational overhead through GitOps automation and infrastructure optimization</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-50 to-pink-50 border-purple-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 15a4 4 0 004 4h9a5 5 0 10-.1-9.999 5.002 5.002 0 10-9.78 2.096A4.001 4.001 0 003 15z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Scalable IoT Integration</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Enabled seamless integration and management of distributed solar PV systems at scale</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-orange-50 border-amber-200">
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-amber-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-amber-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-heading font-bold text-lg mb-2 text-slate-900">Industry Standards Compliance</h3>
                <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm">Achieved full alignment with energy industry regulations and community requirements</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container-custom text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-slate-900">
        Interested in Similar Projects?
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Explore more enterprise architecture initiatives and digital transformation projects
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/portfolio" class="btn-primary">
          View All Projects
        </a>
        <a href="/about" class="btn-secondary">
          Learn More About Me
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
